column12: designer='104.321.93 The tabletop in tempered glass is stain resistant and easy to clean.Handle with care! A damaged edge or scratched surface can cause the glass to suddenly crack or break. Avoid bumps from the side - this is where the glass is most vulnerable.Safety fittings included.'
